attacks.name: Call for Family
attacks.effect: Search your deck for a Basic Pokémon and put it onto your Bench. Shuffle your deck afterward.

attacks.name: Metal Ball
attacks.effect: Put 1 damage counter on the Defending Pokémon.

attacks.name: Recharge
attacks.effect: Search your deck for a Lightning Energy card and attach it to Electrike. Shuffle your deck afterward.

attacks.name: Quick Attack
attacks.effect: Flip a coin. If heads, this attack does 10 damage plus 20 more damage.

attacks.name: Snap Tail
attacks.effect: Choose 1 of your opponent's Pokémon. This attack does 10 damage to that Pokémon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)

attacks.name: Psychic Boom
attacks.effect: Does 10 damage plus 10 more damage for each Energy attached to the Defending Pokémon.

attacks.name: Quick Blow
attacks.effect: Flip a coin. If heads, this attack does 40 damage plus 20 more damage.

attacks.name: Pickup Power
attacks.effect: Search your discard pile for an Energy card, show it to your opponent, and put it into your hand.

attacks.name: Rear Spark
attacks.effect: Does 20 damage to 1 of your opponent’s Benched Pokémon. (Don’t apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)

attacks.name: Knock Away
attacks.effect: Flip a coin. If heads, this attack does 10 damage plus 10 more damage.

cards.name: Energy Search
cards.effect: Search your deck for a basic Energy card, show it to your opponent, and put it into your hand. Shuffle your deck afterward.

cards.name: Potion
cards.effect: Remove 2 damage counters from 1 of your Pokémon (remove 1 damage counter if that Pokémon has only 1).

cards.name: Professor Cozmo's Discovery
cards.effect: Flip a coin. If heads, draw the bottom 3 cards of your deck. If tails, draw the top 2 cards of your deck.
